\cf0 1. Blockchain 
\f2 \uc0\u55357 \u56530 \u55357 \u56599 
\f1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Think of a classroom notebook.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Every time someone scores a point in a game, the score is written in the notebook.\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Once a page is full, everyone gets a copy of that page.\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Nobody can secretly erase or change old scores because everyone has the same copy.\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
New pages are added one after another, making a chain of pages.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 That's basically a blockchain:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Block = a page of records.\
\ls3\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Chain = pages linked together.\
\ls3\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Everyone has a copy, so cheating is very difficult.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Example: If Rahul sends 5 game coins to Priya, everyone can see that transaction was recorded.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
