\cf0 2. Neural Network 
\f2 \uc0\u55358 \u56800 \u55358 \u56598 
\f1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Imagine teaching a robot to recognize cats.\
At first:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
You show it many pictures.\
\ls4\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Sometimes it guesses correctly.\
\ls4\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Sometimes it says a dog is a cat.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Every time it makes a mistake:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
You tell it the correct answer.\
\ls5\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
The robot adjusts its thinking a little.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 After seeing thousands of pictures, it gets really good at recognizing cats.\
A neural network works similarly:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
It learns from examples.\
\ls6\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
It finds patterns.\
\ls6\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
It improves by correcting mistakes.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Think of it as a giant team of tiny decision-makers passing information around until they decide:\
"Yep, that's a cat!" 
