\cf0 1. Blockchain: The Magic Class Notebook 
\f2 \uc0\u55357 \u56538 \u55357 \u56599 
\f1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Imagine your class has a notebook where every student writes down who traded stickers with whom.\
Example:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Rahul gives 2 stickers to Priya.\
\ls8\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Priya gives 1 sticker to Aryan.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Instead of keeping the notebook with one person, every student has an identical copy.\
When a new trade happens:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Everyone checks if it's valid.\
\ls9\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Everyone updates their notebook.\
\ls9\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	3	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Nobody can secretly erase old entries because everyone else would notice.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0
\cf0 What is happening technically?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
A block is a collection of transactions.\
\ls10\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Blocks are connected together in order, forming a chain.\
\ls10\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Each block contains a special digital fingerprint (called a hash) of the previous block.\
\ls10\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
If someone changes an old record, all fingerprints break and everyone knows something is wrong.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Why businesses care\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Banks, supply chains, and companies use blockchain because:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Records are difficult to tamper with.\
\ls11\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Everyone sees the same version of truth.\
\ls11\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Trust doesn't depend on one person.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Simple definition:\uc0\u8232 Blockchain is a shared digital notebook where records are linked together and are very difficult to change.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa321\partightenfactor0
\cf0 2. Neural Network: Teaching a Robot Brain 
\f2 \uc0\u55358 \u56800 \u55358 \u56598 
\f1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Suppose you want a robot to recognize cats.\
You show it:\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f2 \cf0 \uc0\u55357 \u56369 
\f1  Cat 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f1  Correct answer: Cat\uc0\u8232 
\f2 \uc0\u55357 \u56369 
\f1  Cat 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f1  Correct answer: Cat\uc0\u8232 
\f2 \uc0\u55357 \u56374 
\f1  Dog 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f1  Correct answer: Dog\
At first the robot makes lots of mistakes.\
Maybe it says:\
"That cat looks like a dog."\
You correct it.\
After seeing thousands of examples, it starts noticing patterns:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Cats have pointy ears.\
\ls12\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Cats have whiskers.\
\ls12\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Cats have certain eye shapes.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Eventually it becomes very good at identifying cats.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0
\cf0 What is happening technically?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
